 "Indianapolis and Fort Wayne.", "This is a part-time position, with the hope of expanding to full-time as the Lord allows.", "We are also open to discussing ways in which the current position could be expanded to", "include other pastoral responsibilities that would justify a full-time position.", "DESCRIPTION", "REQUIREMENTS:", "Maintain a close walk with Jesus and live a life characterized by humility, godliness and", "submission to God\u2019s Word. Pray regularly for the music ministry.", "Plan the worship service each Sunday in conjunction with the preaching pastor. Also be", "available to oversee holiday services, such as Christmas, Good Friday and Easter.", "Attend and lead weekly rehearsals as well as Sunday morning sound checks before the", "worship services.", "Develop a plan for recruiting, assessing and developing new musicians.", "Cultivate a music ministry marked by technical proficiency, artistic quality and spiritual", "vitality in a way that does not draw attention to the music leaders, but instead directs the", "hearts of the congregation to their Creator and Redeemer.", "Strong interpersonal and organizational skills. Ability to function as team player who gets", "along well with others, but who also can enforce expectations for musical competence."], "bbox": [[0.341763, 0.097663, 0.04762899999999998, 0.029622], [0.147059, 0.091902, 0.5506770000000001, 0.036732], [0.147059, 0.159636, 0.14341699999999996, 0.022513], [0.147059, 0.186017, 0.700359, 0.015573], [0.147059, 0.204502, 0.6865840000000001, 0.015573], [0.147059, 0.222833, 0.681459, 0.015573], [0.147059, 0.241316, 0.07108999999999999, 0.015573], [0.147059, 0.272229, 0.675529, 0.015573], [0.147059, 0.29056, 0.6952670000000001, 0.015573], [0.147059, 0.309043, 0.658596, 0.015573], [0.147059, 0.339947, 0.685651, 0.015573], [0.147059, 0.358277, 0.6196300000000001, 0.015573], [0.147059, 0.376608, 0.6105389999999999, 0.015573], [0.147059, 0.395091, 0.23383000000000004, 0.015573], [0.147077, 0.425995